			        <td valign="top" class="tableCell"><span id="speakerTitleCompanyLabel">Head of Arcade Game Publishing, NHN USA</span></td>
		        </tr>
		        <tr>
			        <td valign="top" class="tableCell"><span id="speakerBioLabel">David Moon has extensive experience in the online game industry.  He counts himself fortunate to have had the opportunity to participate in the online gaming explosion that began in Korea in 2000.  At NHN he has headed the company's overseas expansion efforts and global corporate development.  Since 2005, he has worked on planning and launching NHN USA's new English language game portal, focusing on sourcing, localizing and publishing NHN- and 3rd party-developed titles.  David Moon graduated from Brown University with degrees in Mathematics and Political Science.  He holds a Masters in Political Science from the University of California at Berkeley and still retains the fantasy that someday he will someday have the opportunity to complete his doctoral dissertation.</span></td>
